\\n}\\n\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777993663750}]}\n[recv] {\"type\": \"turn_start\"}\n[recv] {\"type\": \"message_start\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [], \"api\": \"openai-responses\", \"provider\": \"OCA\", \"model\": \"gpt-5.5\", \"usage\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"totalTokens\": 0, \"cost\": {\"input\": 0, \"output\": 0, \"cacheRead\": 0, \"cacheWrite\": 0, \"total\": 0}}, \"stopReason\": \"stop\", \"timestamp\": 1777993663759}}\n[assistant-event] thinking_start\n[assistant-event] thinking_end\n[assistant-event] text_start\n[assistant] Implemented the test fix for `org.slf4j:slf4j-jdk14:1.8.0-beta0`.\n[assistant] \n[assistant] Changes made:\n[assistant] - Removed obsolete tests referencing removed `org.slf4j.impl.StaticMarkerBinder` and `org.slf4j.impl.StaticMDCBinder`.\n[assistant] - Added `JULServiceProviderTest.java` covering the SLF4J 1.8 provider API:\n[assistant]   - `JULServiceProvider.initialize()`\n[assistant]   - JUL logger factory exposure\n[assistant]   - marker factory behavior\n[assistant]   - MDC adapter behavior and cleanup\n[assistant] \n[assistant] Files changed:\n[assistant] - Deleted:\n[assistant]   - `tests/src/org.slf4j/slf4j-jdk14/1.8.0-beta0/src/test/java/org_slf4j/slf4j_jdk14/StaticMarkerBinderTest.java`\n[assistant]   - `tests/src/org.slf4j/slf4j-jdk14/1.8.0-beta0/src/test/java/org_slf4j/slf4j_jdk14/StaticMDCBinderTest.java`\n[assistant] - Added:\n[assistant]   - `tests/src/org.slf4j/slf4j-jdk14/1.8.0-beta0/src/test/java/org_slf4j/slf4j_jdk14/JULServiceProviderTest.java`\n[assistant] \n[assistant] I did not run compilation or tests, per instruction.\n[assistant-event] text_end\n[recv] {\"type\": \"message_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0363691242f093410169fa07c0f0f481a086905b733e38c998\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_conte